Immediately:
Study both documents — the Revenue Advisory Script and Discovery as Due Diligence™ — together until every section feels instinctive.
Memorize the funnel audit structure (TOF → MOF → BOF → Fulfillment).
Run your next three discovery calls exactly by the framework. No improvisation.
Weekly:
