Rewrite your SOWs using the client’s own funnel logic and math.
Audit every engagement: Are you owning input only? Have you clearly assigned conversion ownership?
Monthly:
Log your client case studies. Capture before-and-after funnel metrics for each engagement.
Build your proof library — it will later power your social proof-based discovery method.
Revisit this document every month to recalibrate against the fundamentals.
Long-Term:
Once you’ve delivered multiple engagements with consistent outcomes, begin customizing your own version of the script.
Integrate social proof, engagement metrics, and personal tone.
Move from student to operator to advisor — and from operator to partner.
